.\" heirloom-port-status(7)
.TH HEIRLOOM-PORT-STATUS 7 "2026-07-02" "Heirloom Darwin port" "Port ALM"
.SH NAME
heirloom-port-status \- report repository, install, and prefix state
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B make status
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports on three orthogonal axes for the current
.B heirloom-workspace-darwin
working copy:
.PP
.RS 4
.IP "Repo state" 4
Current HEAD SHA + subject; whether the working tree is dirty; any
tag on HEAD.
.IP "Installed state" 4
Whether
.I .install-manifest-\fIpkg\fP.txt
is present; how many files it lists; how many are actually still
present under
.IR PREFIX .
.IP "Prefix inventory" 4
Per-directory entry counts under
.IR PREFIX/bin ,
.IR bin/s42 ,
.IR bin/posix ,
.IR bin/posix2001 ,
.IR ucb ,
.IR ccs/bin ,
.IR lib ,
.IR share/man/5man .
.RE
.PP
Non-destructive; makes no changes.
.SH EXIT STATUS
Always
.BR 0 .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR heirloom-port-install (7),
.BR heirloom-port-verify (7)
